@need_clarification
title: I need more clarification on this approach
tags: economic_aspects

Me: I need more clarification on this approach.

Facilyn: Think of it this way - instead of saying "I want to be wealthy," ask yourself what wealth would give you. Security? Freedom? The ability to help others? That underlying benefit is what belongs in your quality of life statement.

- #economic_aspects

