title: Let me think more about economic well-being
tags: economic_next

Me: Let me think more about economic well-being.

Facilyn: Take your time. Remember, you're describing how you want your economic life to feel and function, not specific dollar amounts or possessions.

Facilyn: The entity as a whole must be prosperous, but so should the individuals within it. What does prosperity mean to you in practical, lived terms?

